title: Don't Forget Who You Are (song)
data: "Don't Forget Who You Are" is a song by the English musician Miles Kane from his second studio album Don't Forget Who You Are.[1][2] It was released on 3 June 2013 as a Digital download in the United Kingdom.  Its B-side, "Get Right", was co-written by Arctic Monkeys frontman Alex Turner,[3] who played bass guitar on the song.  The song is featured on the EA Sports video game, FIFA 14.
